DARKEST HOUR OF THE LABOR BOSSES\"\nARROGANCE OF \"THE LABOR LOBBY,\"\nIN WASHINGTON, \"INSOLENT ATTITUDE\"!\n\u201cFormer Senator Owen Brewster (R.-Me.) told HUMAN\nEVENTS:\n\u201cTHE REUTHER RECESSION IS THE ISSUE. IN\nSHORT, REUTHER\u2014HEADING UP THE WHOLE LABOR\nBOSS AGGREGATION STANDS AS THE MAIN ISSUE\nTODAY.\"\n(Excerpts Reprinted from HUMAN EVENTS, 5 5-58)\nThe question in Washington today is not whether\nthe Democrats are in hot water, but \u201chow hot is the water?\"\nBoiling\u2014say most of those who have tested the intol\nerablebath in which the majority party in Congress threshes\nabout, as GOP leader Knowland continues to demand real\nlabor reform legislation, and Republicans Curtis, Goldwater\nand Mundt echo and re-echo his cry.\n(See DARKEST HOUR, Page 11)\n\"Die as Avalanche Spills from Rail Car\"\n(Detroit suburb)\n\"4 BOYS BURIED BY SALT\"\n\"PALS TRIP LEVER DURING PLAY\"\n\"RESCUERS BATTLE VAINLY TO STEM DEADLY\nTIDE; 2 LADS ESCAPE\"\n(Free Press, 5/15)\nDISOBEYED PARENTS: 'KEEP AWAY\nFROM RR TRACKS' I\nGOD VIA HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nONE BOY, A VICTIM OF IMPURE LUTHERANISM,\nSATAN ROBBED OF MY IMPERATIVE.\nMARVELOUS CHRIST SCIENCE MESSIAH\nTHINKING!\n(See BURIED BY SALT, Page ll)\n\"HIS WISH FULFILLED. BILLY. 12. IS DEAD\"\n(Timet, S/15)\nSO THE DEVIL SAYS I. OF \"CANCER\" I\nBilly Skaggs.\nGOD VIA HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nTHINKING SUFFOCATION I\nPITIFUL, BUT M-Y-T-H-l-C-A-L, MORTAL\nTHOUGHT, ADAM-EVE IMAGE OF COUNTERFEIT,\nBURLESQUE PARENTHOOD, OFFSPRING, etc.\nI, YOUR \u201cFATHER-MOTHER GOD, ALL-HARMON\nIOUS,\" THE ONE R-E-A-L PARENT OF AN ETERNALLY,\nCOMPLETELY POPULATED UNIVERSE, OF\nINCORRUPTIBLE, INVULNERABLE, OMNIPRESENT\nHEAVEN AND ETERNAL LIFE, NEED NO COUNTER\nFEIT, BURLESQUE, HUMAN PARENTHOOD AND\nOFFSPRING!!!\n(See BILLY, 12, IS DEAD, Page 11)\n\"SATAN BOUND,\" CHRIST REJECTING.\nJUDAS JUDAISM. LOSES SON\n\u2014Lawrence O. Wain, 27\nTHE DEVIL TAKING THE BIBLICAL 40 YEARS.\nPLUS I\nGOO TO HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nUNIVERSITY HOSPITAL. ANN ARBOR.\nAN INVOLUNTARY MENTAL ASSASSIN I\nVIA SPIRITUAL MALPRACTICE\u2014LIKE ALL\nMEDICAL HOSPITALS, IN CONTEMPT OF THE\n(See JUDAISM LOSES SON,' Page 11)\nTIGERS IN R. C'DOG HOUSE'I\nTHE DEVIL AND CATHOLIC \"CAPUCHIN\nCHARITY GUILD\"\n17TH ANNUAL BASEBALL DINNER\nHonoring FRANK C. LANE, General Manager,\n\u201cHERB\" SCORE, Cleveland Indians,\nHARVEY R. HANSEN, President,\n'JIM' BUNNING, Detroit Tigers.\"\nGOD VIA HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nCONTRARY TO MY ONE, TRUE, PURE CHURCH,\nTHE CHRIST, SCIENTIST, THE \"SATAN BOUND\"\nR. C. PRIESTS BRAZENLY INDULGE\nIN CIGARETTES, CIGARS, AND PRESENT\nPFEIFFERS. STROKS. AND SCHLITZ BEER\nOF THE DEVIL'S BILLION RACKETS I\nNO ALTERNATIVE, SOFT DRINK, OFFERED.\nICE WATER, YES, THANK YOU,\u2014AND HOT COFFEE.\n(See TIGERS IN 'DOG HOUSE,' Page 11)\nLOU GORDON INTERVIEWS\nDR. NEAL H. SULLENBERGER, TV. Ch. 4.\nSun. Eve., 5/4\nTRAGEDIES OF MEDICAL\n'3.000 DEATHS BECAUSE OF WRONG BLOOD' I\nWRONG PERSONS OPERATED' I\n'WRONG ORGANS REMOVED' I\n\nA generation ago, a psychiatric journal made the state\nment \u2014and confession that hospitals used to have\n'BUSHELS OF OVARIES' THAT SHOULD NEVER HAVE\nBEEN REMOVED FROM WOMEN'S BODIES I\nGOD TO HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nTHE READERS OF MY DETROIT TRIBUNE ARE\nTHOROUGHLY ALERTED TO THE TRAGEDIES,\nPREMATURE DEATHS, THERAPEUTICS, NOT\nDOMINATED BY MY MARVELOUS, IMPERATIVE\nCHRIST, \u201cSECOND COMING,\" T-H-E \"COMFORTER\nWHO WILL TEACH YOU ALL THINGS\" I\u2014\n(See LOU GORDON, Page 11)\n(The following article is Reprinted from\nHUMAN EVENTS, 5-12-58)\nRECESSION: REUTHER SPAWNS\nUNEMPLOYMENT\nREUTHER RECESSION:\n\u201cDon't play footsie with the labor bosses\" is the slogan\nrising above the tumult on Capitol Hill during the past few\ndays. The phrase was coined by Senator Barry Goldwater\n(R.-Ariz.), as he denounced \u201csweetheart\" labor reform pro\nposals (such as that offered by Massachusetts Democrat John\nKennedy) and DEMANDED REAL SURGERY on the GAN\nGRENOUS POWERS OF THE REUTHERS AND HOFFAS.\nThis cry also sums up the even bigger issue today\u2014the\nrecession and how to cure it. For accumulating evidence\nshows that the avarice of labor bosses, particularly Walter\nReuther, has priced commodities out of the market, produc\ning the current customers' strike which makes itself felt\nthroughout the economy.\n(See REUTHER SPAWNS, Page 2)\nTHE RETURN OF OUR LORD\n(Excerpts Reprinted from CHRISTIANITY TODAY.\nVol. 11, No. 15-5-28-58)\nWILLIAM C. ROBINSON\nThe return of our Lord is the New Testament hope. The\nstory of the primitive fellowship begins with the promise\nthat the Jesus who has been taken up shall return in the\nsame manner as he went into heaven. Likewise the preach\ning of the early Church, preserved in Acts 2:35; 3:19-21;\n10:42; 17:31, includes the testimony that he shall reign\nuntil he has overthrown all his enemies and returns as the\nJudge of the living and the dead.\n(See THE RETURN OF OUR LORD, Page 11)\n\"40,000 [Auto] Deaths Laid To\n'Hunan Failures'\nOF THE \"SATAN BOUND\" ADAMS AND EVES.\nTHE NON-CHRIST SCIENTISTS I\nFORTUNATELY, 'DEATH' IS ONLY OF THE\nMYTHICAL ANTI-CHRIST ADAM-EVE PSEUDO,\n'PHONY' CREATION I REALITY IS DEATHLESS I\nETERNALLY HARMONIOUS!\n(See 40,000 DEATHS, Page 2)\n\"BARRIER CRASH FATAL TO OFFICER\"\n(Detroit Timet, S/16)\n\"POLICE FORCE MOURNS OFFICER\nKILLED ON DUTY\"\n(Newt, S/1S)\nROBBED OF BIBLICAL 40 YEARS I\nGOD VIA HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nTHE DEVIL. ADAM-EVE M-Y-T-H. 'A MURDERER,'\n'HORNED IN' VIA \"SATAN BOUND\nNON CHRIST SCIENTIST MESSIAH RELIGION.\nEDUCATION. CULTURE, THERAPEUTICS.\nPOLICE TRAINING. ENTERTAINMENT.\nRECREATION I\n(See BARRIER CRASH, Page 2)\nTribune\nBaprea\u2014ting \u201cOur Father-Mother Gods\u201d our Divine Publisher\nCrusader Tor The Invincible Triumphant Divine Rights of Mao\nDETROIT, MICHIGAN, SATURDAY, MAY 24,~1958\nFEAII NO EVIL\nJQetieve and deceive\nBy ELIZABETH ELLINGTON\nJesus said. \u201cTherefore I say unto you, what things soever\nye desire, when ye pray, believe that ye receive them, ami\nyc shall have them.\u201d (Mark. 11:24)\nThe edventege of longing to be good end true, proves\ntho power of preyor ovor foer end despair.\nIt has been well said, the;\npeace of God passeth all hu-|\nman understanding. This\nknowing, in a small measure,\nd*y by day, dismisses all\nevil and error, which would\nfalsely attach themselves to\nhuman thinking. So this in\ndicates that intelligent think\ning, is greatly needed to\nimbed the Truth in human'\nconsciousness.\nChristian Science teaches:'\n\u201cTHOUGHTS UNSPOKEN\nARE NOT UNKNOWN TO\nTHE DIVINE MIND. DESIRE\nIS PRAYER; and no loss can\noccur from trusting God with\nour desires, that they may\nbe moulded and exalted be\nfore they take form in words\nand deeds.\u201d\n\nTHE BIBLE TELLS US\n\"For vorily I say unto you, I\nThat whosoovor shall say un\nto this mountain, Be thou\nremovad, and be thou cest\nNEVER ALONE\n(Excerpts Reprinted from CHRISTIANITY TODAY,\nVol. 11, No. 15-5-28-58)\nEDWARD L. R. ELSON\nGod is our refuge and strength, a vpry present help\n(Psalm 46:1)\nPerhaps the finest of Luther's greet hymns js EIN FESTE\nBURG, \"A Mighty Fortress.\" Its majestic and thunderous\nproclamation of our faith is e singing symbol of the Refor\nmation. Inspired by Psalm 46, Luther caught up in the\nhymn the very essence of faith, end the fervor end flavor\nof patriotism which he found in the Psalm. This Psalm had\nfortified Luther with courage to defy the whole system of\necclesiastical tyranny in his day, end his hymn has been\nthe bugle cell of our Protestant heritage. Before the mighty\nGod end his marching hosts nothing can stand. Staerk calls\nthis composition \"the most glorious hymn of faith that ever\nwas sung.\"\n(See NEVER ALONE, Page 2) 1\n\"ALL ABOUT MEN\"\n'NAMBY-PAMBY' MATE WOMAN'S NO. 1\nGRIPE\"\n(News, 5/16)\nGOD VIA HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nATTENTION: ADAMS, EVES: NEITHER OF YOU CAN\nFAIL TO DISILLUSION YOUR MATES BECAUSE THE\nDEVIL, THAT PSYCHOPATHIC, ADAM-EVE\n\"MATTER\" M-Y-T-H, WILL, VIA SUFFERING, COMPEL\nBOTH OF YOU, IN MY, GOD'S, SPIRITUALLY\nPSYCHOLOGICAL MOMENT, \"MAN'S EXTREMITY\n(See 'NAMBY-PAMBY/ Page 2)\n\"CATHOLIC CHARITIES-A MORAL\nAND SPIRITUAL MISSION\"\n(Detroit Times, 5/15)\nOOD VIA HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nTHE ALLEGED SPIRITUAL MISSION OF THE\nDEVIL'S R. C. IS A \u201cGHASTLY FARCE\" I, SPIRITUAL\nLUNACY I THE DEVIL'S FRAUDULENT R. C.,\nMATERIALISTICALLY PERVERTED CHRISTIANITY,\nIS \"SATAN BOUND\" HAND AND FOOT\nSIN, DISEASE, AND DEATH, LURK JUST AROUND\nTHE CORNER IN THE LIVES OF ROMAN CATHOLICS I\n(See CATHOLIC CHARITIES, Page 2)\n'RED' SKELTON'S LATE SON\nDEVK'S MATERIA MEDICA. TOO.\nINVOLUNTARY MENTAL ASSASSIN I\nSPIRITUAL MALPRACTICE.\nDEVIL'S R. C. TAKES SKELTON'S\n_ 9 YEAR OLD SON I\nOur readers will recall that many months ego 'R\u00bbd\nSkelton toured Europe with his son.\nTHE POWER, OF THE DEVIL'S VATICAN TO\nSAVE THE BOY WAS Z-E-R-0 111\n\"BMAKING DOWN h, leer, eh\u2018ThTfuner.l of Iheir\nisri, Ikhird, 9, ere Rod end Georgia Skelton. A GOLD\nCRUCIFIX is held by Mrs. Skelton. It was SENT .TO RICH\nARD BY POPE PIUS XII WHEN WORD REACHED THE\nVATICAN THE BOY WAS SINKING.**\n(Those words under International Nows Photo, Detroit\nTimes)\nDETROIT\ninto the see; end shell not\ndoubt in his heart, but shall\nbelieve that those things\nwhich he seith shell come to\npass; he shell have whatso\never he seith.\" (Mark 11:23)\n\nBE STRONG FOR BRIGHT\nSIDE\n\nThere are, however, those\namong us, who do not wish\nhard enough, to think on the\nbrighter side of life. And\nby so many not holding in\nmind higher purposes in life,\nwith reference to a high\nmarked destination, there\ncomes in our midst a col\nlective false belief of condi\ntions in which recessions\nlayoff, sin, and sickness, are\nportrayed as realities.\n\nSTART NOW\nIn the meantime, each in\ndividual who claims any\n(continued on Pago 4)","height":"27963","width":"19002"}}
